{"tid":396912,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇讀緊u既朋友覺得d人唔識食煙好毒？","createTime":"2017-09-12T05:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T10:39:58.000Z","uid":68626,"like":12,"dislike":71,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"101dd33a6550e3e4220f66aaebdb1afd21739323","tid":396912,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:04:41.000Z","msg":"入到大學都正路18歲以上啦<br />\n入到黎緊係要識下朋友玩下<br />\n有班死毒撚<br />\n酒又唔撚識飲<br />\n煙又唔識食<br />\n淨係識摺係個hell到打機<br />\n真係忍唔住笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e456f800c2c3c4051b9f9ce44ce1591841ff415","tid":396912,"uid":100760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:07:13.000Z","msg":"大學啲人真係比較毒，所謂玩就係喺hall到玩啲on9嘢"},{"pid":"2063b05325eb3755336aa5b1f039788b015e6842","tid":396912,"uid":32898,"like":31,"dislike":5,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:08:36.000Z","msg":"傻尻先食煙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be85efea20e7c5a77216334e5090a30516498a4","tid":396912,"uid":50693,"like":18,"dislike":6,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:08:45.000Z","msg":"食煙仲毒啦 毒撚死你呀"},{"pid":"e295ee2e683f22534c0666aa3476377ebcaa371b","tid":396912,"uid":14797,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:17:00.000Z","msg":"你肯早死多謝哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b630650d6ac4b32ca428d5c918c04ffabd4337a","tid":396912,"uid":136002,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:21:29.000Z","msg":"快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e86979ef8461731985ec30184c234a4fde3c12a","tid":396912,"uid":68626,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食煙仲毒啦 毒撚死你呀</blockquote><br />\n識食就要食？<br />\n你夠識食屎 你食唔食呀"},{"pid":"76cdead510a06e95462a79aecd811eaf36431a0f","tid":396912,"uid":37719,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:25:55.000Z","msg":"駁5到......."},{"pid":"485641b15b7af6c076c644136931ec7d6a4f7271","tid":396912,"uid":146033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:30:32.000Z","msg":"慢性自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d6119e9f1804826964e7a3123b8f42920f0a5e","tid":396912,"uid":82764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"樓主比人笑好慘"},{"pid":"a8e345a737f9138b7d6ea96c8ad728ad5670688d","tid":396912,"uid":23610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:10:49.000Z","msg":"好撚on9😂😂食煙咁on9 都拎嚟打j"},{"pid":"7701b7a56702d6b66bb2467f8e02596f0915bf4b","tid":396912,"uid":90392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:17:57.000Z","msg":"祝天下死煙鏟包括樓主, 早日生癌早日超生, 免再遺害世界。"},{"pid":"ed3fd22fc414ed21dd1b6cf35ae68788fb659a06","tid":396912,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T08:57:07.000Z","msg":"樓主個名解釋一切"},{"pid":"b6aa7bc41a9d91ca0670be5128623ce01e9bd07f","tid":396912,"uid":138177,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:39:56.000Z","msg":"在我而言<br />\n識朋友唔係問題<br />\n又煙又酒就大問題<br />\n<br />\n利申：不煙不酒<br />\n格硬講嘅話就吸二手煙同飲過一啖啤酒"},{"pid":"8106f38ad56e12b5c5e0c96cea993dbf22982441","tid":396912,"uid":479,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T09:43:13.000Z","msg":"住hell緊係要食in la🚬"},{"pid":"8e1ff4d8d987212eafe63b40496d9df64a6c2603","tid":396912,"uid":24547,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺批評其他人唔關心政治/時事既人好撚ON9 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios \" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363050/page/1?ref=ios </a> - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n回未呀OP <br />\n走場不要得<br />\n<br />\n順手回埋le部分<br />\n原文<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span> 係定義<br />\n好似叫<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人</span>係<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER</span>一樣<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">前因</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">後果</span><br />\n<blockquote>不當類比<br />\nNIGGER=負面+黑人 黑人=黑人<br />\n但黑人一定=NIGGER NIGGER都一定=黑人<br />\n故此 黑人=黑人 NIGGER=黑人<br />\n所以無問題<br />\n你要PROOF 到無立場=負面 咪比你話無立場=港豬囉<br />\n港豬=無立場 但無立場唔一定係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人=NIGGER 係視乎講個個人咩心態<br />\n黑人係任何時候都可以=NIGGER<br />\n就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span><br />\n有主觀情感 呢個答案滿唔滿足到你<br />\n無立場係咪任何時候都係負面?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">黑人（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">NIGGER(事實+負面)</span> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(事實+負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(事實+中性)</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無立場（事實）</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬(事實+負面)</span><br />\n以上三者均是係<span style=\"color: red;\">事實</span>=事實+觀感<br />\n而例子1,2均係由洗手兄提出同接受<br />\n<br />\n而係以如此邏輯之下<br />\n洗手兄不斷要在下回答&quot;無立場係咪任何時候都係負面&quot;<br />\n一點可見 洗手兄本末倒置<br />\n將 負面 定性為 <span style=\"color: red;\">無立場</span>=<span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span><br />\n嘅必要條件 而非 <span style=\"color: gold;\">港豬</span>嘅附加觀感<br />\n<br />\nLong story short<br />\nIf<br />\n無立場係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係港豬<br />\n<br />\n黑人係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係Nigger<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係負面 先可以話係傻仔<br />\n<br />\n智力低於80係任何時候都係中性 先可以話係智能障礙<br />\n<br />\n不過洗手兄又話<br />\n<blockquote>就好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">智力低於80</span> 你可以話佢<span style=\"color: gold;\">傻仔(負面)</span>/<span style=\"color: gold;\">智能障礙(中性)</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">所以無立場係咪任何時候都係負面 同無立場=港豬<br />\n係完全irrelevant </span>"}]}